general.desc: Island Information & Technology Inc engages in the provision of information technology services. It offers products and services such as computer hardware, software and other related products. The company provides services related to the Internet and computer networks. The company covers product development, licensing, marketing, sales and resale, distribution, operations and upgrading of and maintenance of computer software.
